        title: "Overview",
        text: "Hi! My name is Henrique Rocha, but you can call me Rique. I'm a full-scholarship Computer Engineering student at Insper and the first person in my family tree to attend university. /n I've interned as a Software Engineering intern at BASF's global headquarters in Ludwigshafen, Germany, achieving a 20x performance optimization on a global analysis pipeline. I studied at the Technische Hochschule Ingolstadt (THI), traveled through 12 countries and 51 European cities during my exchange, and returned to Brazil to found Startellite — a platform that connects startups with top software engineers. /n This page tells my whole story, from the very beginning.",
