        title: "Family Background",
        text: "Before telling you who I became and the path I've taken, let me share a bit about my origins: I was born into a Christian household where my parents serve God in the Congregação Cristã no Brasil (CCB), where I've been a violinist since 2018. My father was born and raised in the countryside of Bahia, having only studied through 5th grade, and works at a wholesale market. My mother is from São Paulo and studied nursing at a technical level, always striving to work at better hospitals. As soon as I got into Insper, she felt motivated and started a college nursing degree. I have a twin brother who received a ProUni scholarship to study Architecture and Urban Planning at Mackenzie University, and a younger sister in elementary school.",
